	column 'Aging Distribution' = ```
			
			SWITCH(
			    TRUE(),
			    'Open Mems'[Aging] <= 5," Within 5 Days",
			    'Open Mems'[Aging] > 7,"Over 7 Days",
			    'Open Mems'[Aging] > 5,"Over 5 Days"
			    
			)
			```
		lineageTag: 74f0f785-e871-43e1-badc-9dd21dbe6256
